            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="18606291">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">认识一个人的唯一方式是不抱希望地去爱那个人。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-05-30 19:47</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">13人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>认识一个人的唯一方式是不抱希望地去爱那个人。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

